990"},{"product_id":"capricorn-charm","title":"Capricorn Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eReliability and perseverance are core characteristics of a capricorn. Once its trust is won, it will stay loyal and never let you down. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is available in 18 karat gold and sterling silver.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"18 karat Gold","offer_id":53848304091482,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Sterling Silver","offer_id":53848304124250,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Capricorn-gold.jpg?v=1773993908"},{"product_id":"pisces-charm","title":"Pisces Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eWith creativity and intuition pisces follow the transformations in life effortlessly. Their natural connection to their inner feelings and their empathy for others make them a sensible character, living between reality and imagination.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is available in 18 karat gold and sterling silver.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"18 karat Gold","offer_id":53844723335514,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Sterling Silver","offer_id":53844723368282,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Pisces-gold.jpg?v=1773926147"},{"product_id":"aries-charm","title":"Aries Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eAlways up for a challenge and a fresh start, aries is full of energy and enthusiasm. With its great optimism and the concentration on the positive side, for this star sign everything is reachable.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is available in 18 karat gold or sterling silver.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"18 karat Gold","offer_id":53844594819418,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Sterling Silver","offer_id":53844594852186,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Aries-gold.jpg?v=1773924629"},{"product_id":"taurus-charm","title":"Taurus Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eDown to earth but with a weakness for luxury, a taurus is reliable and solid as a rock. Living in the here and now, it makes the best out of everyday life instead of dreaming up castles in the air.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is available in 18 karat gold and sterling silver.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"18 karat Gold","offer_id":53844558152026,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Sterling Silver","offer_id":53844558184794,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Taurus-gold.jpg?v=1773923747"},{"product_id":"gemini-charm","title":"Gemini Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eCurious and talkative, you will never get bored with a gemini! As they are always well informed about the latest trends and love to entertain, their energy and optimism is inspiring and contagious. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'San Francisco', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eThis pendant is available in 18 karat gold and sterling silver.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"18 karat Gold","offer_id":53843805339994,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Sterling Silver","offer_id":53843805372762,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Gemini-gold-marble.jpg?v=1773911654"},{"product_id":"cancer-charm","title":"Cancer Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eA very sensitive character, cancers have great intuition and empathy and deeply care about their beloved ones. Nonetheless, they are determined and ambitious to reach their life goals.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is available in 18 karat gold and sterling silver.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"18 karat Gold","offer_id":53843438993754,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Sterling Silver","offer_id":53843439026522,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Cancer-gold.jpg?v=1773922738"},{"product_id":"leo-charm","title":"Leo Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eCharismatic and generous, everyone is attracted by Leo's magnetic field. As a natural leader this star sign will take care of the well being of his family and beyond and loves the recognition for these efforts.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eThis pendant is available in 18 karat gold and sterling silver.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"18 karat Gold","offer_id":53843407700314,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Sterling Silver","offer_id":53843407733082,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Leo-gold.jpg?v=1773912779"},{"product_id":"virgo-charm","title":"Virgo Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eDeeply connected to the earth, a virgo takes decisions according to analytical reasoning and practical considerations. Striving for meaningfulness in life, this star sign has an authentic and strong character.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is available in 18 karat gold and sterling silver.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"18 karat Gold","offer_id":53843299336538,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Sterling Silver","offer_id":53843331580250,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Virgo-gold.jpg?v=1773912892"},{"product_id":"paperclip-chain","title":"Handmade Paperclip Chain","description":"\u003cp\u003eA handmade, 18 karat gold necklace. Worn on its own it adds a \u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003etouch of minimalistic elegance to any outfit. In combination with your favourite \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/collections\/pendants\"\u003ependants\u003c\/a\u003e it becomes the expression of your personal style and your story. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eAs all LURI pieces, this necklace is crafted entirely by hand.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Schuberthan Gold","offers":[{"title":"45 cm","offer_id":49892760813914,"sku":"","price":1450.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"55 cm","offer_id":49892760846682,"sku":"","price":1650.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC1676.jpg?v=1731433154"},{"product_id":"golden-heart-pendant","title":"Golden heart pendant","description":"\u003cp\u003eAn everyday reminder of love, affection and support, this pendant in 18 karat gold is the perfect gift. It is available with the gemstone of your choice, but strong also on its own. Here pictured with a garnet, the birthstone of January. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/pages\/contact\"\u003eContact\u003c\/a\u003e me, together we will find the right gemstone for you. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LURI jewels","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53684041449818,"sku":null,"price":220.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/heart-of-gold-garnet-1.jpg?v=1772028284"}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/collections\/DSC1784.jpg?v=1763111512","url":"https:\/\/luri.gold\/collections\/pendants.oembed","provider":"LURI jewels","version":"1.0","type":"link"}